languages.text: Товарооборот надолго замирает. Варп-аномалия совершает долгое путешествие от системы к системе, будто выискивая жертв, а затем исчезает без следа.
Trade grinds to a halt for a long time. The warp anomaly slowly makes its journey from system to system, as if looking for victims, before vanishing without a trace.

traits.locale_text: Trade grounds to a halt for a long time. The warp anomaly slowly makes its journey from system to system, as if looking for victims, before vanishing without a trace.
Warp energies disfigure the earth and people in the area. Having gathered their bloody harvest, the sorcerous powers disappear without a trace.

traits.locale_text: Le commerce est durablement interrompu. L'anomalie du Warp progresse lentement de système en système, comme si elle cherchait de nouvelles victimes, avant de disparaître sans laisser de traces.

languages.text: 貿易は長い間停止していた。〈歪み〉の異常は、まるで犠牲者を探すかのように、ゆっくりと星系から星系へと旅を続け、やがて跡形もなく消えていった。
languages.original_text: Trade grinds to a halt for a long time. The warp anomaly slowly makes its journey from system to system, as if looking for victims, before vanishing without a trace.

traits.locale_text: 貿易は長い間停止していた。〈歪み〉の異常は、まるで犠牲者を探すかのように、ゆっくりと星系から星系へと旅を続け、やがて跡形もなく消えていった。

languages.text: 贸易停顿了很长一段时间，亚空间异常从一个星系慢慢飘到另一个星系，仿佛在寻找猎物一样。到了最后，它消失得无影无踪。
languages.original_text: Trade grinds to a halt for a long time. The warp anomaly slowly makes its journey from system to system, as if looking for victims, before vanishing without a trace.

languages.text: El comercio se detiene durante mucho tiempo. La anomalía de disformidad viaja de un sistema a otro, como si buscara víctimas, antes de desaparecer sin dejar rastro.
languages.original_text: Trade grinds to a halt for a long time. The warp anomaly slowly makes its journey from system to system, as if looking for victims, before vanishing without a trace.

traits.locale_text: El comercio se detiene durante mucho tiempo. La anomalía de disformidad viaja de un sistema a otro, como si buscara víctimas, antes de desaparecer sin dejar rastro.

languages.text: Der Handel kommt für lange Zeit vollkommen zum Erliegen. Die Warp-Anomalie reist langsam von System zu System, als würde sie nach Opfern suchen, bevor sie spurlos verschwindet.
